<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="vision-n">vision <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'vɪʒn/    美 /'vɪʒn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>视力；视觉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have <strong>good / poor vision</strong>
视力好/差</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>想象；幻象</strong></h4>
<p>a picture in your imagination：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>give her a <strong>vision of</strong> her future
带给她对未来的憧憬</p><footer>2009 上海</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>远见：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a man of great vision
具有远见卓识的人</p></div></div>